Mobile::Messaging::ParlayX - Interface to SonyEricsson SMS/MMS Gateway
======================================================================

DOCUMENTAION

For a detailed documentation see the man page:

   man Mobile::Messaging::ParlayX

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   XML::LibXML
   LWP::UserAgent
   HTTP::Request

